This is a simple mod. It replaces maleheadwarpaint_01.dds, maleheadwarpaint_02.dds, & maleheadwarpaint_03.dds with Kabuki style facepaints. 

I\\\'m not done with this yet, and will be adding more when the mood strikes me. I just wanted to post what I have so far. These are NOT STANDALONE so make sure you backup any facepaints you already have.

Usage: Place folder \\\"Data\\\" from the rar into your Skyrim directory, and play!
